attribs.name: repeating_action_-KEmGmDZZI3Ugr1XLQbY_content
attribs.current: This attack can originate from the frozen soul or any creature possessed by split soul.

attribs.name: repeating_action_-KEmH69Rv-3AkEJvlpIO_content
attribs.current: Sacrifice half its current hp and launch a chilling mist at one creature in DC 17 Charisma saving throw, on a save the possession is resisted the target immune for 24 hours and the frozen soul loses that hp. On a fail it regains the hp as well as replacing the target with that split hp as temporary hp becoming a split soul (max two). If used on a corpse it does not make a  save. Possession ends when the temporary hp is reduced to 0 or the frozen soul ends the possession as a bonus action

attribs.name: repeating_legendaryaction_-KEmIP6EZt2S5Wd9qplk_content
attribs.current: 2 Legendary Actions - Make two split souls swap places.

attribs.name: repeating_legendaryaction_-KEmIZCkamxR6m99xZGZ_content
attribs.current: 3 Legendary Actions - Ice chains attempt to restrain a target within of itself or a split soul. DC 17 Dexterity saving throw or be restrained. DC 17 athletics check to break free as an action.

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KEmEoRN19IWye1OC9YZ_content
attribs.current: Bonus action to target a creature it can see within 5 ft that has 0 hp to make a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or die creating a frozen soul regaining [[1d12]] hp per hitdie the target has.

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KEmEpm5sEoLLOgBZz9i_content
attribs.current: Can move through narrow space as small as 1 inch wide and can move through objects and people. Touching the creature sustain (1d10) cold damage or having it share the same space causing the same damage.
